data.description: Beautiful GOLF COURSE LOT! Located in Palm Valley Phase 1, this move in ready home has been updated with a NEW HVAC and New Roof with warranty! Granite Countertops in the kitchen with Smooth Glass Top Stove. Built in Microwave & Refrigerator included. Living Room & Family Room shares a nicely updated 2-way fireplace. Quartz countertops in all bathrooms and upgraded tiled walk-in shower in primary bedroom. Plenty of Storage throughout home with Ample space in each guest bedroom. Primary bedroom has it's own private balcony that looks over the well maintained Golf Course & meticulously designed and landscaped backyard. This home is located in area with a lot of conveniences and easy access to the I-10.
